{"tid":2068363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"設計師網上發佈警員資料判監28日獲緩刑　葛珮帆批判刑過輕應上訴","createTime":"2020-06-17T15:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T01:13:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b1f48e7118ba68671b49f651bad6e58b1cec4f","tid":2068363,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"一名女設計師去年11月在在社交平台刊載警員及其家屬的個人資料，<span style=\"color: red;\">早前在高等法院承認違反禁制令，早上被判監28日，<strong>獲緩刑一年</strong></span>，並須向律政司支付3萬元的訟費，是首宗違反相關禁制令的案件。律政司表示，會研究法庭判詞，然後決定是否需要跟進。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時，同意須判即時監禁，但接納被告品格良好，真誠悔過，因此判監28日，緩刑一年。民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆批評法官判刑過輕，變相鼓勵滋事分子繼續起底，對公眾有深遠影響，促請律政司考慮就判刑提出上訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312274&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1312274%26csid%3D261_341&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=27e18934\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1312274&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"305e00997d2442cebbc396f575688a87b5c0bae8","tid":2068363,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"設計師網上披露警員資料干犯禁制令 判囚28天緩刑一年<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2067505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2067505</a>"},{"pid":"1097765718d2c48169ab454332ec520117997783","tid":2068363,"uid":307619,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"6ae37b7122fb3ae5c9919beacbcd5a85b8eb689e","tid":2068363,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"假博士死開啦<br />\n自己友就可以輕判"},{"pid":"39b84c0173c0beceacdab9cf7d0bd841810680fa","tid":2068363,"uid":268519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2HLYcN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2HLYcN.jpg&h=321de10c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8wwTL8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8wwTL8.jpg&h=5a7f4c90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E8rHEw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E8rHEw.png&h=54a0cd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6S4ujA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6S4ujA.jpg&h=974c13ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0OfAZH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0OfAZH.jpg&h=d5ff3d7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"286e34109d8a43164e397ebed4206ccacb2ae8e0","tid":2068363,"uid":212626,